| Limit | Value |
|---|---|
| Max duration | {/* e.g. 10s */} |
| Min duration | {/* e.g. 1s */} |
| Resolutions | {/* e.g. 720p, 1080p */} |
| Aspect ratios | {/* e.g. 16:9, 9:16, 1:1 */} |
